This paper is likely to belong to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category as it deals with detecting sarcasm in text. Additionally, it may also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as the paper presents Machine Learning and Deep Learning approaches for sarcasm detection. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) may also be a likely sub-category as the paper deals with analyzing text data. Finally, Cybernetics (cs.CY) may also be a possible sub-category as the paper deals with the challenges of detecting sarcasm in numerical portions of text.
